A Window Film Warranty Management application built in CakePHP

Warranty has a ManyToMany relationship to Products, with a join table of WarrantyProducts containing extra
information about the relatioship, such as Square Footage.

Warranty also contains several Users, including the Dealer selling the Product, the Installer and the Customer

Based on a series of rules, provided by the client, a Warranty may be automatically approved and a PDF of the terms
emailed to the Customer. If a Warranty is not automatically approved, an administrator from the client will be
tasked with making a determination and Approving or Denying the Warranty application.

In some cases, a Warranty may contain a Glass Protection rider which covers window glass in case the original
window warranty is voided by applying the client's Product.